Alembic migrations for ERP Nam Phuong.

Common commands:

  alembic current
  alembic heads
  alembic upgrade head
  alembic revision -m "short_description"

Rules:

- Do not edit production database schema manually when a migration can be written.
- Keep every migration file in backend/alembic/versions/.
- Test upgrades on a fresh local database before merging.
- If a migration depends on seed data, document that seed step in docs/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md.
